445
00:28:14,884 --> 00:28:18,095
Olhem só, o Don Vidrine
e o Bob Kaluza.

446
00:28:18,096 --> 00:28:20,950
- Bem-vindo, Sr. Jimmy.
- Pois.

447
00:28:21,057 --> 00:28:24,704
