513
00:31:51,267 --> 00:31:52,935
- Muito obrigado.
- Tenha um bom dia.

514
00:31:52,936 --> 00:31:54,539
Igualmente.

515
00:31:58,233 --> 00:31:59,961
Sr. Williams?

516
00:32:01,361 --> 00:32:03,172
